      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "HI ELLEN (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (17.70) last time in a Grade 4/5 at this track. Form here sound including four wins. The form out of last race has been strong. Has winning claims on her best figures. WHERE'S THE BOSS (2) has a strong record here with five wins and four placings from 15 starts. Was out of placings last time (20.46) at Grafton in a Grade 5, finishing fourth and beaten 7 lengths. Looks well placed here and among the chances. LADY BLAZINGTON (6) flew the lids from out wide with a slick early split but ran over at the finish when a narrow fifth (17.20) over 300m at this track. Yet to taste defeat from two runs out of this box. Has ability and can measure up. LOOKS A PICTURE (8) is worth another chance despite missing the top-three here most recently.",
